result.formatted_address: 27-33 Hau Wong Road, Hau Wong Rd, Kowloon City, Hong Kong
result.name: EASTAR Restaurant

reviews.text:
Excellent service and food! If you're a Western hungry carnivorous, try the "American mixed grilled," which consists of a mountain of tender meat in your plate! (Chicken breast, pork, beef, a hot dog sausage and bacon, with mashed potatoes and broccoli!) 

I had the vegetable curry which was also very fulfilling... And excellent.

With our meals, the nice waitress brought us delicious soups and bread, in less than 2 minutes, along with drinks that were included, and a tiny surprise dessert!

(Great place to discover in Kowloon among all the other places we haven't tried! )
Food is meh but great service.
价錢合理，黑毛豬好正。
呢間餐廳太唔掂啦，枱燈污糟裝修殘夠，我食咗隻豬手都有啲霉霉地，侍應態度OK，但係啲餐具亂咁放，老婆話茶餐廳不如，不是一間西餐廳，最重要係琴晚食完之後肚屙。
地點價錢合宜，但想似酒店排場或水準不是這種。
